{"article_id":"mAoaLw02YMmcuAaJ","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Lynda LaCasse ,","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"who was one of Reade ' s neighbors in California ,","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"where Reade moved","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"after working for Biden ,","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"said in an interview with Business Insider","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"published Monday","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"that Reade told her in the mid-1990s","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"that Biden had \" put his hand up her skirt","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"and he put his fingers inside her . \"","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"Lorraine Sanchez , a former colleague of Reade ' s in the office of a California state senator , also told the news outlet","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"that Reade told her in the mid-1990s","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"that she \" had been sexually harassed by her former boss","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"while she was in DC","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"and","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"as a result of her voicing her concerns to her supervisors ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"she was let go , fired. \"","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"Sanchez did not recall","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"whether Reade mentioned Biden specifically ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"or whether she provided further details about the allegation .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"In recent days , a 1993 call into Larry King ' s CNN talk show also surfaced .","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"In it , a woman","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"whom Reade identified as her now-deceased mother called","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"to report unspecified \" problems \"","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"her daughter was having with her employer ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"whom she called \" a prominent senator. \"","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"The caller said","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"her daughter did not want to go public with her account \" out of respect for \" the unnamed senator .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Neither LaCasse nor Sanchez responded to messages","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"left by The on Monday .","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"Reade made the harassment accusation last year ,","depth":4},{"id":30,"text":"and she recently offered details of what she said","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"was a sexual assault in a hallway somewhere on Capitol Hill .","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"The allegations have percolated for weeks , a period","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"in which Biden has become the presumptive Democratic presidential nominee .","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"Three of Reade ' s supervisors from the time ,","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"to whom Reade says","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"she complained about Biden ' s behavior ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"have said","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"they don ' t remember Reade or any complaints from her .","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"Biden ' s campaign declined to comment on the new reports ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"pointing to previous statements from deputy campaign manager Kate Bedingfield ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"who said","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"that while women ' s accounts of wrongdoing should be examined ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"the one from Reade \" absolutely did not happen . \"","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"As part of an in-depth examination","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"published two weeks ago ,","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"Reade had told The Post","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"that she described the alleged assault soon afterward to a friend , to her brother and to her mother .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Her friend corroborated Reade ' s account of their conversation","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"but declined to be named .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"Her brother , Collin Moulton , told The Post","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"that she told him in 1993","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"that Biden had behaved inappropriately","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"by touching her neck and shoulders .","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"He said in a later text message to The Post","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"that he recalled her telling him","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"that Biden had put his hand \" under her clothes . \"","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"Biden has done several interviews","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"since the assault allegations emerged","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"but has yet to be asked about them .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"It has , however , been a topic for other top Democrats ,","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"including some of his potential running mates .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"\" I think","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"this case has been investigated , \"","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"Sen. Amy Klobuchar","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"( D-Minn. )","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"said on MSNBC ,","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"pointing to her own work","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"to make it easier to bring such cases forward .","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"\" I know the vice president as a major leader on domestic abuse .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"I worked with him on that . \"","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"Michigan Gov . Gretchen Whitmer","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"( D ) ,","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"who has said","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"she was sexually assaulted while in college ,","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"was asked on NPR","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"if she was concerned about the allegations .","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"\" Well , I think","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"women should be able to tell their stories .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"I think","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"that it is important that these allegations are vetted , from the media to beyond .","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"And I think","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"that ,","depth":15},{"id":83,"text":"you know ,","depth":16},{"id":84,"text":"it is something","depth":17},{"id":85,"text":"that no one takes lightly , \"","depth":17},{"id":86,"text":"Whitmer said .","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"\" But it is also something","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"that is ,","depth":15},{"id":89,"text":"you know ,","depth":16},{"id":90,"text":"personal .","depth":16},{"id":91,"text":"And so it ' s hard to give you greater insight than that ,","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"not knowing more about the situation . \"","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"Trump has been accused by more than a dozen women of sexual assault .","depth":4},{"id":94,"text":"He has denied all of the allegations .","depth":4},{"id":95,"text":"His son Donald Trump Jr. has repeatedly tweeted about the accusations against Biden in recent days .","depth":5},{"id":96,"text":"On Monday afternoon , he retweeted the Business Insider story .","depth":5},{"id":97,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"( R-Ky. )","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"said Monday","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"that the allegations against Biden deserve to be scrutinized as much as those against Supreme Court Justice Brett M. Kavanaugh ,","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"who during his nomination hearings was accused of a past assault .","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"\" I think","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"these things ought to be dealt with symmetrically , \"","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"McConnell said on Fox News Radio .","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"Reade worked in Biden ' s Senate office from December 1992 until August 1993 ,","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"according to employment records .","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"She had initially said last year","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"that Biden had put his hands on her shoulders and neck .","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"She said","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"she complained to senior Biden aides about feeling uncomfortable ,","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"but not about sexual assault .","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"She also said","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"she filed a complaint with a congressional human resources or personnel office ,","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"which could have triggered an alert to Biden ' s office .","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"The Post interviewed a number of former Biden staffers","depth":5},{"id":116,"text":"who say","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"the behavior","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"Reade describes","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"was not consistent with Biden ' s behavior .","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"Last spring ,","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"as Biden was preparing to run for president ,","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"about a half dozen women came forward with stories of unwanted touching or displays of affection .","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"None alleged sexual assault .","depth":6},{"id":124,"text":"LaCasse told Business Insider","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"that Reade tearfully told her about the alleged encounter in 1995 or 1996 ,","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"when they were neighbors in a condominium complex in Morro Bay , Calif .","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"LaCasse said","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"the allegations came on her radar again only recently ,","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"when Reade contacted her","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"and remarked","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"that \" this Joe Biden thing is coming up again . \"","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"She said","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"that she spoke with Reade about coming forward ,","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"\" but she didn ' t really ask me to come forward . \"","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"LaCasse also said","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"that she was planning to support Biden in the general election .","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"\" I can ' t stand Donald Trump ,","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"so I don ' t want him to win , \"","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"she told Business Insider .","depth":7},{"id":140,"text":"\" But this happened ,","depth":6},{"id":141,"text":"and I know","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"it did","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"because I remember talking about it . \"","depth":7}],"relation